{"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionProtocol","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GPropertyAction"},{"type":"text","text":" is a way to get a [iface"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Action"},{"type":"text","text":"] with a state value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"reflecting and controlling the value of a [class[Object](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/object] property.","type":"text"}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Protocol","fragments":[{"text":"protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"PropertyActionProtocol"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO22PropertyActionProtocolP","symbolKind":"protocol","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"role":"symbol","title":"PropertyActionProtocol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PropertyActionProtocol"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"inheritsFrom","kind":"relationships","title":"Inherits From","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol","doc:\/\/GIO\/4GLib14PointerWrapperP","doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP"]},{"title":"Conforming Types","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyAction","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionRef"],"kind":"relationships","type":"conformingTypes"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/propertyactionprotocol"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"protocol"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"PropertyActionProtocol","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ActionProtocol","preciseIdentifier":"s:3GIO14ActionProtocolP","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/ActionProtocol"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ObjectProtocol","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The state of the action will correspond to the value of the property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Changing it will change the property (assuming the requested value"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"matches the requirements as specified in the [type"},{"identifier":"\/\/documentation\/gobject\/paramspec]","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Only the most common types are presently supported.  Booleans are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"mapped to booleans, strings to strings, signed\/unsigned integers to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"int32\/uint32 and floats and doubles to doubles.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the property is an enum then the state will be string-typed and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conversion will automatically be performed between the enum value and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"‘nick’ string as per the [type[EnumValue](\/\/documentation\/gobject\/enumvalue] table."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Flags types are not currently supported."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Properties of object types, boxed types and pointer types are not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"supported and probably never will be."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Properties of [type[Variant](\/\/documentation\/glib\/variant] types are not currently supported."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"If the property is boolean-valued then the action will have a ","type":"text"},{"code":"NULL","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"parameter type, and activating the action (with no parameter) will"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"toggle the value of the property."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In all other cases, the parameter type will correspond to the type of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"the property.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The general idea here is to reduce the number of locations where a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"particular piece of state is kept (and therefore has to be synchronised","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"between). "},{"code":"GPropertyAction","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" does not have a separate state that is kept","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in sync with the property value — its state is the property value."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"For example, it might be useful to create a [iface","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Action","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"] corresponding"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to the "},{"code":"visible-child-name","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property of a "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/docs.gtk.org\/gtk4\/class.Stack.html"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"so that the current page can be switched from a menu.  The active radio","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"indication in the menu is then directly determined from the active page of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GtkStack"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An anti-example would be binding the "},{"code":"active-id","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property on a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/docs.gtk.org\/gtk4\/class.ComboBox.html","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":". This is"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"because the state of the combo box itself is probably uninteresting and is"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"actually being used to control something else."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Another anti-example would be to bind to the ","type":"text"},{"code":"visible-child-name","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"property of a ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"GtkStack","identifier":"https:\/\/docs.gtk.org\/gtk4\/class.Stack.html","overridingTitleInlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GtkStack"}]},{"type":"text","text":" if"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"this value is actually stored in [class","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Settings"},{"text":"].  In that case, the","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"real source of the value is* [class","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Settings","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"].  If you want"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a [iface"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Action","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"] to control a setting stored in [class","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/Settings","type":"reference"},{"text":"],","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"see [method"},{"code":"Gio.Settings.create_action","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] instead, and possibly combine its"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"use with [method"},{"code":"Gio.Settings.bind","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionProtocol"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol exposes the methods and properties of an underlying "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GPropertyAction"},{"type":"text","text":" instance."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The default implementation of these can be found in the protocol extension below.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"For a concrete class that implements these methods and properties, see ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyAction","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Alternatively, use "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionRef","type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" as a lighweight, "},{"code":"unowned","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" reference if you already have an instance you just want to use.","type":"text"}]}]}],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionProtocol\/property_action_ptr-1054s"],"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionProtocol\/bind(property:to:_:flags:transformFrom:transformTo:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionProtocol\/get(property:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/PropertyActionProtocol\/set(property:value:)"],"anchor":"Instance-Methods","title":"Instance Methods"}],"references":{"doc://GIO/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/10GLibObject0B8ProtocolP","title":"GLibObject.ObjectProtocol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/PropertyActionProtocol":{"title":"PropertyActionProto